tm1hb">麻生将国防开支的增加和恢复与韩国总统尹成烈的穿梭外交视为岸田政府的成就。 “这是一个作为领导人无疑取得了成就并采取了务实措施的内阁，”他说。</p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 10:19:20 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUA1676X0W3A510C2000000/</guid><link/> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUA1676X0W3A510C2000000/<category> G7广岛峰会</category><category>政治</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[はごろもフーズ、ツナ原料の下処理 海外移管 原料高で]]></title><description><![CDATA[<img src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352779016052023000000-2.jpg?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;ch=Width%2CDPR&amp;crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;fp-z=1&amp;h=186&amp;ixlib=java-1.2.0&amp;w=300&amp;s=c183a41930bbb332c2fcfaff360136a3" title="" alt="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb"> <a href="https://www.nikkei.com/nkd/company/?scode=2831" data-track-article-link="true">Hagoromo</a> Foods 将把部分金枪鱼制造流程转移到海外以削减成本。将金枪鱼、鲣鱼等原料去皮去骨的前处理工作，从日本的主要工厂之一的烧津工厂（静冈县烧津市）移交。加工原料从国内进口，加工成金枪鱼罐头。该公司将简化国内生产并应对高昂的原材料成本。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">将金枪鱼和鲣鱼的头、尾、骨切开，鱼肉蒸凉，去细骨的过程……</p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 10:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOCC09C5Z0Z00C23A5000000/</guid><link/> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOCC09C5Z0Z00C23A5000000/<category>中部</category><category>静冈</category><category>服务/食品</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[菅前首相、31日にも訪韓 尹大統領との会談調整]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">据报道，自民党前首相兼日韩议员同盟会长菅义伟计划31日访问韩国。我正在协调与 Yoon Seok-yeol 总统的会谈。本来预定5月中旬访问，结果流产了。 16日，官员说。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">关于日韩关系，岸田文雄首相将于7日和8日访问韩国，恢复两国领导人之间的全面“穿梭外交”。副知事麻生太郎也在11日访韩会见了尹总，与议员的交流日趋活跃。 〔联合的〕</p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 10:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOCD17AWE0X10C23A5000000/</guid><link/> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOCD17AWE0X10C23A5000000/<category>政治</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[企業年金の特別法人税撤廃の声 厚労相の諮問機関会合で]]></title><description><![CDATA[<figure class="center_c1symtaw figure_f1xkd112 figure_fv30jf" data-image-viewer-target="true" data-src-for-image-viewer="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3354386017052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=680&amp;h=510&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=62a2770a3dab29b7cb10325b61e2b7da"><div class="pictureWrapper_p13ffdka" style="max-width:638px"><div style="max-width:638px"><picture class="picture_p169s49k" style="padding-bottom:75.07836990595611%;width:638px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3354386017052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=479&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=a998006a85eab47b1cf8f198985d34c5" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3354386017052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=479&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=a998006a85eab47b1cf8f198985d34c5" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3354386017052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=450&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=98530b51f6d0edfd877adcd7d720a238" media="(min-width: 752px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3354386017052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=450&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=98530b51f6d0edfd877adcd7d720a238" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3354386017052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=450&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=98530b51f6d0edfd877adcd7d720a238" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3354386017052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=479&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=a998006a85eab47b1cf8f198985d34c5" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1">相关机构的听证会（17日，东京）</figcaption></div></div></figure><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">厚生劳动省将审查民间养老金制度，为 2024 财年的养老金制度修订做准备。 17日召开了社会保障会议（厚生劳动大臣的咨询机构）相关分会，听取了民间年金管辖相关机构的意见。有人呼吁取消对储备金征收的特别公司税。厚生劳动省将在夏季前后多次召开类似的会议来解决问题。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">私人养老金包括企业养老金，如企业型定额缴费养老金（企业型DC）和个人养老金，如个人型定额缴费养老金（iDeCo）。在会议上，企业年金基金联合会和企业年金联络委员会呼吁废除特别企业税，认为海外很少有储备基金本身需要征税的情况。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">作为iDeco执行机构的国民年金基金联合会要求它加强推荐加入iDeCo，提高订阅者的便利性，并简化行政程序。该委员会的一名成员指出，“必须有一个系统来确保企业年金和 Ideco 等各种系统的用户之间的公平性。”</p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 10:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUA171FX0X10C23A5000000/</guid><link/> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUA171FX0X10C23A5000000/<category>经济的</category><category>税收/预算</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[納税はキャッシュレスで 埼玉りそな銀が支店でイベント]]></title><description><![CDATA[<figure class="center_c1symtaw figure_f1xkd112 figure_fv30jf" data-image-viewer-target="true" data-src-for-image-viewer="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3356193017052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=680&amp;h=425&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=76aa45e5fb4cd9162889682e6953cbb1"><div class="pictureWrapper_p13ffdka" style="max-width:638px"><div style="max-width:638px"><picture class="picture_p169s49k" style="padding-bottom:62.539184952978054%;width:638px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3356193017052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=0ef76019cee146163c2ac7d43cd87992" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3356193017052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=0ef76019cee146163c2ac7d43cd87992" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3356193017052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=70dc1348990c4f16a27e1a7742c3d794" media="(min-width: 752px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3356193017052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=70dc1348990c4f16a27e1a7742c3d794" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3356193017052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=70dc1348990c4f16a27e1a7742c3d794" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3356193017052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=0ef76019cee146163c2ac7d43cd87992" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1">大野知事在县政府接受无现金支付的说明（埼玉市，17 日）</figcaption></div></div></figure><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">埼玉 Resona 银行将于 19 日至 19 日在其县支行（埼玉市）等地举办特设展位活动，让客户体验无现金支付的便利。指导非当面缴费方式，推进税收征管数字化。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">在活动的第一天，即 17 日，小野元博知事访问了县政府并在听取了如何无现金支付的讲座的同时缴纳了汽车税。该行行长福冈聪也到场监督知事的纳税情况。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">与面对面支付相比，无现金支付需要更少的文书工作。除了简化银行和政府的运作外，纳税人还可以在方便的时间付款，而无需考虑地点。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">福冈总统说：“整个经济都在数字化，无现金变得越来越普遍。我们有责任与埼玉县合作以促进便利。”除了县政府分行，该银行还在其浦和中央分行、浦和美园分行、南浦和分行和与野分行推广无现金支付。</p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 10:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOCC174S30X10C23A5000000/</guid><link/> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOCC174S30X10C23A5000000/<category>埼玉</category></item></channel></rss>